T1  - Negotiating Relationally: The Dynamics of the Relational Self in Negotiations
AU  - Gelfand, Michele J.
AU  - Major, Virginia Smith
AU  - Raver, Jana L.
AU  - Nishii, Lisa H.
AU  - O'Brien, Karen
Y1  - 2006/04/01
PY  - 2006
DA  - 2006/04/01
